@delventhalz @taylorpage New changes made -- ready for another review!

A new collection is automatically generated when a user signs in with a private key that the system hasn't yet seen. (Actually, a new collection is attempted to be generated every time, but as it doesn't affect anything for returning users, we won't tell returning users what we're doing.)

Upon login, a user will be redirected automatically so that they'll be viewing their collection.

